content.html: I used to care that people respected my work in DevRel as “real” engineering work. Now I just don’t care. And I can’t tell if that’s personal growth, apathy or survivorship bias. Probably everything. Anyway I work in marketing and create value whether or not you recognize it.
content.value:
I used to care that people respected my work in DevRel as “real” engineering work.

Now I just don’t care.

And I can’t tell if that’s personal growth, apathy or survivorship bias.

Probably everything.

Anyway I work in marketing and create value whether or not you recognize it.
